name: Self Portrait Processing the Cyberlinguistic Soft-Chatter [Cryptoborg #18]
description: The embedded soft-chatter chip is a high-end cyberlinguistic data-distributor for the rapid networking  (and conversion) of C-langs threatened with immanent extinction. Every day on earth an estimated two hundred C-Langs are lost due to decimal-zoom time-scaling errors and quantum malfunctions in semiotic-loop addresses.
